  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3014207">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3014207/" class="title-link">如饮好茶，回味无穷</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3014207"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/13117209/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u13117209-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/13117209/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">牛小花</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-25 11:16:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3014207_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        看到豆瓣上很多友人的评价，几乎都说此乃考研必备之书，我了解此书也是在考研时期，无奈，那是自己反而心浮气躁，不能静心阅读，走马观花的看过，对立面插图倒是赞口不绝，我买的是当时的最新版，包装之精美价位，图片印刷很清晰，让人看着就很舒坦。     作者论述的方式...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3014207/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3014207_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3014207_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



